The '''wineseller''' is an unnamed minor character in the [[Season 1|first season]]. He is played by guest star [[Simon Lowe]] and only appears in &quot;[[You Win or You Die]].&quot; He attempts to poison [[Daenerys Targaryen]] in the markets outside [[Vaes Dothrak]], as King [[Robert Baratheon]] of Westeros has promised a lordship for doing this. He is discovered, captured, and executed.
